data.description: Welcome to Washington's Arizona come and enjoy our 300 days of sunshine,  mild winters, Great fishing and boating just down the road. Not to mention Golfing, Summer concerts, Grand Coulee Dam, Fishing, hunting, and Views from every window of this home.  Custom Built home on 5 acres situated next to State land 1748 sq ft Ranch style, Custom Cabinets,  High tech wiring,  Double car garage, Large Primary Bedroom with a custom tile shower,  Decks on both the front entry and back for viewing the wildlife or just relaxing and taking in all the sunshine.  This location has so much to offer with all the local lakes and recreation come visit Eastern Wa.
